## Testing

For critical packets, include hex dump tests:

```rust
#[test]
fn test_encode_creature_health() {
    let packet = encode_creature_health(0x12345678, 100);
    assert_eq!(packet, &[0x8C, 0x78, 0x56, 0x34, 0x12, 100]);
}
```
